         <div>
            <head>"POEM"</head>
            
            <lg>
               <l>Being walkers with the dawn and morning</l>
               <l>Walkers with the sun and morning,</l>
               <l>We are not afraid of night,</l>
               <l>Nor days of gloom,</l>
               <l>Nor darkness,</l>
               <l>Being walkers with the sun and morning.</l>
            </lg>

            <byline>-Langston Hughes.</byline>
         </div>
